# Building Modern React Applications

Modern React development has evolved significantly with the introduction of hooks and the concurrent features in React 18.

## Key Patterns

### Custom Hooks

Extract reusable stateful logic into custom hooks:

```js
function useDebounce(value, delay) {
  const [debouncedValue, setDebouncedValue] = useState(value);
  useEffect(() => {
    const handler = setTimeout(() => setDebouncedValue(value), delay);
    return () => clearTimeout(handler);
  }, [value, delay]);
  return debouncedValue;
}
```

### Context for Global State

For lightweight global state, React Context works well. For complex state, reach for Zustand or Jotai.

## Conclusion

The ecosystem has matured — pick the simplest tool that solves your problem.
